---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of Service for Eazy.Family — the family organizer app.">
  <div style="max-width: 44rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 8rem 1.25rem 4rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 3rem;">Last updated: May 2025</p>
    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Acceptance</h2>
      <p>By using Eazy.Family, you agree to these terms. If you don't agree, please don't use the service.</p>

      <h2>The service</h2>
      <p>Eazy.Family provides a family organizer platform including shared calendars, task lists, messaging, and an AI assistant. The service is provided "as is" and we may update or modify features over time.</p>

      <h2>Your account</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You must be 16 or older to create an account</li>
        <li>You are responsible for keeping your account credentials secure</li>
        <li>One account per person — do not share accounts</li>
        <li>You may not use the service for any illegal purpose</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Your content</h2>
      <p>You own the content you create in Eazy.Family. By using the service, you grant us a limited license to store and display that content to you and your family members as part of operating the service. We do not claim ownership of your content.</p>

      <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
      <p>You agree not to use Eazy.Family to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Harass, abuse, or harm other users</li>
        <li>Share illegal content</li>
        <li>Attempt to access other users' accounts or data</li>
        <li>Reverse engineer or scrape the service</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Free tier &amp; paid plans</h2>
      <p>Eazy.Family offers a free tier. Additional features may be available on paid plans. Pricing and features may change with reasonable notice.</p>

      <h2>Termination</h2>
      <p>We may suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms. You may delete your account at any time.</p>

      <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>Eazy.Family is not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the service.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@eazy.family">hello@eazy.family</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
